---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Granny Flats Carrum Downs | Modular, Cost-Effective | (03) 9003 0108"
  description="Granny flat builders for Carrum Downs — 1990s-2010s estates, smaller 400-700m² blocks, cost-conscious modular builds. VicSmart fast-track pathway. Free design consultation."
  canonical="https://frankstongrannyflats.com.au/carrum-downs/">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Carrum Downs &middot; Sandfield &middot; Lyrebird</span>
      <h1>Granny flats in <span class="accent">Carrum Downs</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Carrum Downs is mostly 1990s and 2000s estates &mdash; 400&ndash;700m&sup2;
        blocks, modern slab-on-ground homes, mortgage-belt demographic. Granny flats
        here are usually the cost-effective modular option, fast-tracked through
        VicSmart, sized to fit the rear yard without losing the lawn.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Book a free consultation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Why Carrum Downs</span>
      <h2>The Carrum Downs granny flat story.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div style="max-width: 65rem;">
        <h3>Block size dictates the design.</h3>
        <p>
          Most Carrum Downs blocks fall in the <strong>450&ndash;650m&sup2;</strong> range.
          Frankston City still allows one second dwelling per lot &ge;300m&sup2;, but the
          rear setback, outdoor space requirement, and existing house siting mean a
          realistic granny flat is 35&ndash;50m&sup2; for a 1-bedroom. Anything bigger
          starts eating the main dwelling&rsquo;s required outdoor area.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Modular is usually the right call.</h3>
        <p>
          Carrum Downs streets are narrow, side access is often via a 3m gate or no
          access at all. Custom on-site build means hand-walking materials through
          the existing house or carrying over the fence &mdash; expensive and risky
          for the existing landscaping. <strong>Factory-built modular</strong> craned
          in from the street is faster, cheaper, and doesn&rsquo;t trash the lawn.
          12&ndash;16 weeks from contract to keys.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Cost-conscious doesn&rsquo;t mean low-spec.</h3>
        <p>
          Carrum Downs buyers want value, not budget compromises that cost more later.
          Our standard Carrum Downs spec includes <strong>NCC 2022 / 7-star NatHERS
          compliance</strong>, double-glazed windows, R4 ceiling insulation, ducted
          reverse-cycle heating/cooling, and induction cooktop. Total: $110K&ndash;$140K
          installed for a 1-bedroom modular. The cheap version skips the ducting and
          single-glazes — costs you $40/month forever in winter heating.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Typical Carrum Downs jobs.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>1-bedroom modular 40m&sup2;, VicSmart fast-track, $115K&ndash;$135K all-in</li>
          <li>2-bedroom modular 70m&sup2; (where block size allows), $160K&ndash;$190K</li>
          <li>Crane-in delivery from kerbside, 1-day install</li>
          <li>Adult-child accommodation with separate driveway access</li>
          <li>Side-yard demolition + replacement (older 1990s shed cleared)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>Other service areas.</h2>
      <div class="areas-grid">
        <a class="area-pill" href="/frankston-south/">Frankston South</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/mt-eliza/">Mt Eliza</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/mornington/">Mornington</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/seaford/">Seaford</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/mornington-peninsula/">Mornington Peninsula</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Free Carrum Downs design consultation.</h2>
        <p>Modular crane-in. VicSmart fast-track. Honest cost-vs-value advice.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Book online</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
